Package: nodbi
Title: 'NoSQL' Database Connector
Description: Simplified document database manipulation and analysis,
    including support for 'NoSQL' databases ('Elasticsearch',
    'CouchDB', 'MongoDB'), 'key-value' databases ('Redis'), and other
    'NoSQL' types ('etcd').
